<item>
            <title>[BATCH-1363] Job stopped in split state does not finish with status = STOPPED</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/BATCH-1363</link>
                <project id="10090" key="BATCH">Spring Batch</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The analysis on the forum post isn&apos;t quite correct because SimpleFlow is used even for sequential executions.  The problem lies in the SplitState: it needs to unwrap ExecutionExceptions and re-throw their cause.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
